summary: This is a 100% clean save taken just after leaving the cave from Helgen.
descriptionHtml:
This clean save using a freshly installed Steam version of Skyrim (1.9.32.0.8 - October 2013) references only Skyrim.esm and Update.esm

It should be suitable for anyone who desires a completely pristine beginning for testing or other purposes.  The save was made right upon exiting the cave after Helgen, escorted by Hadvar.

Enjoy!
author: Pharnham
